Non-programmer here with a team struggling a bit on that end.

About two years ago we found out about needing to use command based in order to use the NavX. So the team tried to tackle that and haven’t gotten it to really ever work.

Closest we got was a bot that drove backwards.

I’ve given them the deadline of Saturday that they need to demonstrate a functioning drive base with one extra motor. If that can’t happen they have to go back to time based.

It’s using PV with April tags out of the question with timed?
